```plantuml
@startuml UnoSD_UnoCash

actor User
participant "Blazor Frontend" as Blazor
participant "Azure Functions Backend" as Backend
participant "Azure Blob Storage" as BlobStorage
participant "Azure Form Recognizer" as FormRecognizer

User -> Blazor: Access UnoCash Application
Blazor -> Backend: Request Home Page Data
Backend -> Backend: Process GetExpenses
Backend -> Blazor: Return Expense Data

User -> Blazor: Upload Receipt Image
Blazor -> BlobStorage: Upload Image
BlobStorage -> Blazor: Return Upload Success

Blazor -> Backend: Request Receipt Processing (SAS Token)
Backend -> BlobStorage: Generate SAS Token
BlobStorage -> Backend: Return SAS Token
Backend -> FormRecognizer: Analyze Receipt Image
FormRecognizer -> Backend: Return Parsed Data

Backend -> Backend: Cache Receipt Data
Backend -> Blazor: Return Receipt Data

User -> Blazor: Add/Edit Expense
Blazor -> Backend: AddExpense/UpdateExpense
Backend -> Backend: Process Expense Data
Backend -> Blazor: Confirm Operation

@enduml
```